---
layout: default.njk
title: News & updates – ORRA
---

<section>
  <h2>News &amp; updates</h2>
  <p>
    News, updates and our regular newsletter, with the latest on local issues,
    events and what the committee has been working on.
  </p>
  <p>
    <a href="/feed.xml">Subscribe via RSS &rarr;</a>
  </p>
</section>

{% for post in collections.news | reverse %}
<section>
  <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
  <p class="post-date">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</p>
  {% if post.data.summary %}<p>{{ post.data.summary }}</p>{% endif %}
</section>
{% endfor %}
